---+ Flaws
---++ Unreferenced
   * Number of references &#10004;
   * Lexical features (word prefix) &#10004;

---++ Orphan
   * Incoming links < 3 &#10004;

---++ Refimprove
   * Number of tokens &#10004;
   * Ratio: text_length/number_of_references &#10004;
   * Ratio: sentences/references &#10004;
---++ Empty Section
   * Number of words in section = 0 &#10004;
   * Number of words in section &#10004;
---++ Notability
   * In/outlinks &#10004;
   * Footnotes
   * Tag: proposed deletion (see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:Notability) &#10004;
   * Number of sections &#10004;
   * Number of tokens &#10004;
   * Revision features (age, number of revision etc.) &#10004;
---++ No footnotes
   * Footnotes = 0
   
---++ Primary Sources
   * Revision features &#10004;
   * Lexical features(unigrams, bigrams) &#10004;
   * Number of references &#10004;
   
---++ Wikify
   * Number of wikilinks
   * Revision features
   * Ratio: plain_text/markup_text
   * Number of different markup elements (number of sections etc.)
   * Section length
---++ Advert
   * List of ad words
   * Lexical features (unigrams, bigrams)
   * Page parameters (locked page etc.)
   * Last modification by unregistered user?
---++ Original research
   * Revision features
   * Lexical features
   * Number of references
   * Ratio: number_of_references/text_length

---+ Revision Features
   * Page age
   * Number of reviews
   * Number of reviews per user
   * Number of reviews by registered users
   * Number of reviews by experienced users
   * Number of discussions posted
   * Modified lines rate
 
 
